reviewText: Glad I got it, great music with genre's and great camera work. The shorts were fun to watch as well

I WAS EXPECTING MORE FISHING COVERAGE AND NOT SO MUCH GETTING THEIR. SEEEMED TO ME A LOT OF TALKING BETWEEN PEOPLE AND THAN SHORT PIECES OF SOMEONE CATCHING A FISH. DIDN'T GRAB ME LIKE SOME OF HIS PREVIOUS FILMS. LIKED SHORT FILM SECTION OF TAPE...
